data.description: Explore this well-maintained two-story townhome offering modern comforts and convenience. Enjoy granite kitchen countertops, a deck, and a fireplace in a carpet-free space. Stainless steel appliances and a Samsung washer/dryer are included. Nearby HEB adds convenience, while key destinations like the Medical Center, USAA, and UTSA are just a short drive away. HOA provides access to a swimming pool and basketball court.     Listing agent has an ownership interest in the property
